sources.contents: {"dev:app":"yarn workspace @sigma-audiobooks/app start","dev:server":"yarn workspace @sigma-audiobooks/server start","build:app:dev:device":"cd packages/app && eas build --platform ios --profile dev:device","build:app:preview:device":"cd packages/app && eas build --platform ios --profile preview:device","build:app:dev:simulator":"cd packages/app && eas build --platform ios --profile dev:simulator","build:app:preview:simulator":"cd packages/app && eas build --platform ios --profile preview:simulator"}
